Subject: [PATCH] Gentoo Changes

---
 Makefile      |  44 -----------------
 mscs          |   4 +-
 mscs.defaults | 132 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 mscs.initd    |  22 +++++++++
 4 files changed, 156 insertions(+), 46 deletions(-)
